{"word":"κωλύω","slug":"κωλύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰωλύω</el></b> [<el>ϰόλος</el> ‘with a part lopped off’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘stop (someone) from doing (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>)’, <b>prevent <a href='B:470 19:14'>Mt 19:14</a>; <a href='B:480 9:38'>Mk 9:38f</a>; <a href='B:490 11:52'>Lk 11:52</a>; <a href='B:510 8:36'>Ac 8:36</a>; <a href='B:510 16:6'>16:6</a>; <a href='B:520 1:13'>Ro 1:13</a>; <a href='B:530 14:39'>1 Cor 14:39</a>; <a href='B:590 2:16'>1 Th 2:16</a>; <a href='B:610 4:3'>1 Tim 4:3</a>; <a href='B:650 7:23'>Hb 7:23</a>; <a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 10</a>.</b> Cp. <b><a href='B:680 2:16'>2 Pt 2:16</a>.</b> In related sense<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp> withhold <a href='B:490 6:29'>Lk 6:29</a></b> (transfer of an object is prevented); <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sim.\">sim.</a> <b><a href='B:510 10:47'>Ac 10:47</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κῶλον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κώμη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}